  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe, \u0bb2\u0bb9\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bail for three including Ratta and Lahiru",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "\"Kota Ko Kama\" activists Lahiru Weerasekhara, Hon. Ratkarave Jinaratne Thera and YouTuber Rathindu Senaratne alias Ratta have been released on bail.",
        "They have been arrested and remanded in connection with the violent incidents that took place during the demonstration in Colombo last June 09.",
        "They were wanted for offenses such as unlawful assembly in front of the police headquarters in Colombo and causing damage to public property and obstructing the duties of police officers during the protest.",
        "They were arrested after surrendering at the Maradana police station and have been remanded till today by the Fort Magistrate's Court.",
        "It is noteworthy, however, that the Fort Magistrate's Court today released them on personal bail."
      ],
